    <p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:35.45pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:baseline;'><span style='font-size:16px;;'>4) комплекс&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:16px;;'>QRS</span><span style='font-size:16px;;'>&nbsp;расширен</span></p>
